	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is there any emulator or tool that converts Action Replay Codes to Game Genie codes. I am asking because i have Action replay codes for monster in my pocket and i dont have emulator with action replay support.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


